Package InstagramDownloader

Class FromInstagram

  • java.lang.Object
    • InstagramDownloader.FromInstagram
  • public class FromInstagram
extends java.lang.Object
    This very small library fetches video and image files from Instagram, without using any API or provided key. To work this library properly, you need to download JSoup library.
    Author:
    Alan Hammoud
